Dawit Seyaum Biratu (amụrụ na 27 Julaị na afọ 1996) bụ onye Etiopia na-agba ọsọ n'etiti etiti nke na-ahụ maka 1500 mita. Ọ nọ n'ọkwa nke anọ na 2015 World Championships wee merie ọlaọcha na 2016 World Indoor Championships
Dawit nwetara ọla nchara na mita 5000 na 2022 World Championships.
Dawit nọ na mmemme ọkachamara ya na 2013 World Youth Championships ihe rite ọla ọcha ya na 2014 World junior champion.

Dawit Seyaum mere mmetụta mbụ ya na ọkwa mba n'afọ 2013, na-emeri 1500m mba junior title. Oge izizi ya na IAAF Diamond League circuit sochiri n'oge na-adịghị anya mgbe nke ahụ gasịrị, o setịpụkwara ihe kacha mma nke onwe ya nke 4:14.95 nkeji na Doha Diamond League. A họpụtara ya maka nke mbụ ya na mba ụwa na 2013 World Youth Championships in Athletics ma bụrụ onye nke abụọ na Tigist Gashaw 意 na oge mbụ Ethiopia were ebe abụọ kachasị elu na ihe omume ahụ. Ọ gbanwere ọnọdụ a na 2013 African Junior Championships, na-ewere aha ahụ na nkeji 4:09.00 ọtụtụ sekọnd n'ihu Tigist.
2018 World Indoor Championships nke e mere na Birmingham enweghị ihe ịga nke ọma n'ihi na e wepụrụ ya na okpomọkụ.

N'ọnwa Febụwarị na afọ 2022, Dawit setịpụrụ oge kachasị n'ụwa nke 8:23.24 maka mita 3000 n'ime ụlọ na Meeting Hauts-de-France Pas-de-Calais na Liévin, na-aghọ nwanyị nke atọ kachasị ọsọ na ihe omume ime ụlọ a n'akụkọ ihe mere eme (naanị ndị obodo ya Dibaba na Gudaf Tsegay gbara ọsọ ọsọ). Ọ mechara nke ise na ihe omume ahụ na 8:44.55 na World Indoor Championships na Belgrade n'ọnwa na-esote.
